column1: Analysis of lens pairs for optical remote focusing.
All distances are in mm (except wavelengths : in nm), angles are in degree, RMS wavefront error is in waves
WARNING : if your lenses files don't take into account the reduction of lens diameter due to their mounting, the cut-off angle can be overestimated !
WARNING : Coating is not taken into account, please check if your lenses are designed for the right wavelengths !
WARNING : Always check if lenses were imported with correct materials, and if raytracing diagram and wavefront seems correct ! (especially when pair have negative ffl and/or bfl)
